    <h1>Should You Try to Avoid AI Detection? An Honest Look</h1>
    <p class="description">Trying to avoid AI detection is a losing game. Learn why detection evasion hurts your content, what to focus on instead, and how to use AI ethically.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">SG</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
